{"id": "25770", "post": "<div class=\"post-25770 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dedicated-servers category-virtual-servers tag-black-friday tag-cheapwindowsvps tag-hosterlabs tag-hyper-expert tag-knownhost tag-limitless tag-misaka tag-parkinhost tag-quadranet tag-servarica tag-servermania tag-softshellweb tag-teradelta\" id=\"post-25770\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/special-awards-for-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Special Awards for Black Friday/Cyber Monday Offers</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/black-friday/\" rel=\"tag\">black friday</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/cheapwindowsvps/\" rel=\"tag\">cheapwindowsvps</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hosterlabs/\" rel=\"tag\">hosterlabs</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hyper-expert/\" rel=\"tag\">Hyper Expert</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/knownhost/\" rel=\"tag\">knownhost</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/limitless/\" rel=\"tag\">limitless</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/misaka/\" rel=\"tag\">misaka</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/parkinhost/\" rel=\"tag\">parkinhost</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/quadranet/\" rel=\"tag\">QuadraNet</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servarica/\" rel=\"tag\">servarica</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servermania/\" rel=\"tag\">servermania</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/softshellweb/\" rel=\"tag\">softshellweb</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/teradelta/\" rel=\"tag\">teradelta</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> December 3, 2020 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p>Some previous posts about 2020 Black Friday/Cyber Monday in case you missed them:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/did-you-miss-any-of-these-amazing-black-friday-offers/\">Black Friday Recap</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/did-you-miss-any-of-these-amazing-cyber-monday-offers/\">Cyber Monday Recap</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/top-ten-lowendbox-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers/\">Top Ten Offers</a></li></ul><p>In this post, I\u2019d like to hand out some special awards for providers whose offers were interesting, unique, different, or otherwise stood out from the pack this year.&nbsp; It\u2019s not always about providing the lowest price-per-GB (though sometimes it is!).&nbsp; Providers can differentiate themselves in others ways, so let\u2019s take a look at some of the interesting offers.</p><p><strong>Best Green Hosting Offers</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/black-friday-with-green-hosting-hoster-labs-stops-by-from-the-north-pole-2gb-ipv6-only-vps-for-1-50-mo/\">Hosterlabs</a> runs of 100% renewable power and offered a 1GB VPS for 99 cents/month</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/softshellweb-turns-black-friday-green-with-offers-in-taiwan-us-eu-taiwan-vps-from-30-year-eu-us-from-20-year/\">SoftShellWeb</a> offered to plant a tree for every month of service you have with them.&nbsp; And they had cool Black Friday office pics in their post as well!</li></ul><p><strong>Best High Bandwidth Offers</strong></p><ul><li>Hard to top <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servermania-offers-big-managed-dedis-with-100tb-of-bandwidth-starting-at-99-mo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ServerMania</a>\u2018s mammoth 100TB offer!</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/serverhubs-cyber-monday-offer-includes-50tb-bandwidth-dedis-e3s-in-la-dallas-elsewhere-starting-at-27-month/\">ServerHub</a> dropped a 50TB bandwidth offer</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/quadranet-exclusive-black-friday-dedi-offers-in-los-angeles/\">QuadraNet</a> offered dedis with 30TB of bandwidth</li></ul><p><strong>Best Massive Storage Offer</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lions-mammoths-and-black-friday-offers-oh-my-servarica-is-here-4gb-for-10-mo-in-canada/\">ServaRICA</a>\u2018s 8TB of SSD for $20/mo was pretty amazing</li></ul><p><strong>Best Exotic Locale</strong></p><p>OK, these aren\u2019t exotic like \u201cAntarctica\u201d or \u201cPyongyang\u201d but places we don\u2019t see often:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/welcome-parkinhost-cyber-monday-specials-in-russia-50-all-vps-offers-including-1gb-for-3-85-mo-on-annual/\">ParkInHost</a> debuted some offers in Russia</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/softshellweb-turns-black-friday-green-with-offers-in-taiwan-us-eu-taiwan-vps-from-30-year-eu-us-from-20-year/\">SoftShellWeb</a> brought us an offer in Taiwan</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/internoc24-has-an-offshore-hosting-cyber-monday-offer-in-kazakhstan-from-e4-mo-on-annual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Internoc24</a> had our first offer ever in Kazakhstan</li></ul><p><strong>Best Debut With a Custom Panel</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/misaka-debuts-for-black-friday-custom-control-panel-1gb-vps-for-25-year-in-virginia/\">Misaka</a> showed us their cool mc2 panel</li></ul><p><strong>Best Windows Service</strong></p><p>I\u2019m a Linux/OpenBSD guy myself but some people like Windows.&nbsp; If you\u2019re one of those, then\u2026</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/cheap-windows-vps-best-offer-ever-54-yr-4gb-kvm-or-99-yr-8gb-kvm-vps-over-50-off/\">CheapWindowsVPS</a> had a great Windows offer</li><li>And so did <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/racknerd-brings-a-true-black-friday-offer-kvm-vps-in-9-locations-from-8-89-year-including-amd-ryzen-nvme-windows-vps/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RackNerd</a></li></ul><p><strong>Absolute Low Price Awards</strong></p><ul><li>For shared in US/EU, cheapest I saw was <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/limitless-hosting-black-friday-special-includes-3-year-shared-hosting-plus-vps-reseller-deals/\">Limitless</a> offering DirectAdmin for $3/year</li><li>For shared in Asia/Pacific, the nod goes to <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/cybermonday-usa-cpanel-shared-hosting-for-4-25-year-from-teradelta-or-7-25-year-in-singapore/\">TeraDelta</a>\u2018s $7.25/year offer in Singapore</li><li>For VPS,&nbsp;the obvious choice is <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/black-friday-hyperexpert-blows-the-doors-out-with-a-1gb-vps-for-1-year/\">Hyper Expert</a>\u2018s 1GB VPs for $1/year!</li></ul><p>Once again, <strong>many thanks to our providers</strong> for bringing us such wonderful diversity in the marketplace.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/top-ten-lowendbox-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Top Ten LowEndBox Black Friday/Cyber Monday Offers\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Top Ten LowEndBox Black Friday/Cyber Monday Offers</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/did-you-miss-any-of-these-amazing-cyber-monday-offers/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Did You Miss Any of these